  op $cont-instantiate-r0-c0 : SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals SpectecTerminals -> Config .
